l gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Registration</stro=
ng> =E2=80=94 not required for protection to exist, though required before =
you can sue for infringement in federal court, and required within certain =
timeframes to claim statutory damages and attorney's fees.</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>The =C2=A9 notice<=
/strong> =E2=80=94 not required since the US joined the Berne Convention in=
