<ul class=3D"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:l=
ast-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-co=
l gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Common law copyrig=
ht</strong> protected <em>unpublished</em> works, essentially indefinitely,=
 under state law.</li>
<li class=3D"whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Federal statutory =
copyright</strong> kicked in upon <em>publication</em>.</li>
</ul>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
