igations the person who leaked it had.</p>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]">But here's the kicker you identified earlier =E2=80=94 trade secret=
 protection evaporates on genuine public disclosure. If the formula were tr=
