cally depending on circumstances of disclosure.</p>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]"><strong>The thing nobody actually cares about</strong></p>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]">You're right that nobody cares about the physical document. And cop=
yright law, almost poetically, only protects the thing nobody cares about =
=E2=80=94 the specific expression on paper =E2=80=94 while explicitly refus=
