nalysis is actually more nuanced than that.</p>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]"><strong>Trade secret misappropriation requires wrongful acquisition=
 or knowing use</strong></p>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]">Not everyone who encounters leaked information on GitHub is automat=
ically liable. The Uniform Trade Secrets Act and the federal Defend Trade S=
ecrets Act (DTSA, 18 U.S.C. =C2=A7 1836) both require that the misappropria=
tion involve:</p>
<ul class=3D"[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:l=
ast-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-co=
